				<section id="KitchenGardening">
					<div class="">
						<h4>Kitchen Gardening</h4>
						<p>As Goshen’s we encourage households to grow green leafy vegetables in kitchen gardens for sustainable balanced diet. Kitchen gardens are easy to manage since they are within the household vicinity and do not required much space. Harvests from kitchen gardens can as well be sold by the households to earn an income.</p>
						<p>As Goshen’s we support households start sack/kitchen gardens and give them vegetable seedlings, empty sacks and training as startup kits.</p>
					</div>
